reviews_data.review_text: I had the Matcha Blueberry Bliss off the Spring menu today and it was out of this world. The matcha and blueberry complement each other incredibly well. And the barista who made it was lovely! I’ll be back for sure!!

We stopped by in the afternoon for a girls hockey game and got a raspberry white chocolate mocha, and it was amazing!! Highly recommened! We got chocolate chip cookies to share and they were great too. Shoutout to Emmi for being a great barista!
This place is awsome the staff made special meals for the academy would recommend to everyone
This place is awsome the staff made a special menu for the academy. I will recommend everyone to this place
GO INSIDE! The coffee and tea is great and the staff lovely. You might think you’re in the wrong place but you’re not. Great prices too!
They weren't open like it was advertised.
Delicious coffee and friendly staff, what more do you need?
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for stopping by! We loved having you!

reviews_data.review_text: This place was an amazing little surprise to find in a roller rink. Got a latte and a breakfast sandwich and they were both beyond what I imagined they would be. Definitely worth checking out!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for your review!! We’re glad you stopped by :)
